title: Super clean and spacious 2 bed 2 bath apt in Atlanta
posting_body: ['Super clean and spacious 2 bed 2 bath apt in Atlanta, Offering an unexpected abundance of outdoor space, this home is fronted by a large shared patio, and leads to the show-stopper of a rooftop terrace.', 'This Newly Painted two Bedroom Apartment is located on a quiet block.', 'Bedrooms w/closets (can fit king), kitchen incl stove and new refrigerator with room for a bistro or small table, living room, an area for office space or dinette, large closet off kitchen, fully tiled bathroom w/shower.', 'Rent includes utilities, premium fios cable, wifi and central air.', 'Great neighborhood.', 'Cats OK Dogs with landlord approval.', 'Recently renovated apartment.', 'Upper-level unit in a small complex with excellent off-street parking.', 'pets ok.', 'Rent includes water, sewer, trash and recycling.', '$745 per month.', 'Off street parking.', 'Large shared yard space.', 'Utilities, lawn maintenance and snow removal are the responsibility of the tenant.', 'Upper-level unit in a small complex with off-street parking.', 'The handsome stone and steel kitchen overlooks the chic living room, with a fireplace, exposed brick, hardwood floors and a built-in desk and shelves.', 'The second floor bedroom is surrounded by large windows and sliders with Juliet balconies, a newly tiled three-piece bath and convenient full-size laundry Massage me now if you are really interested: Give me your contact number.']
